title: Keep on getting matched with junglers who die to their fucking camps.
body: Yesterday, I got a Nid jg in my game who died to her fucking red buff, not at lvl 1, think she died to a different camp atleast 1 more time. Today, I got 2 more of these fuckers, why am I getting these? Is it because of my elo? My account is more than halfway to lvl 200.
